Summary: Took two pictures at random and found something in one photo
divs: Sighting DetailsI look at MUFON.com everyday and I always see peoples finding by just finding something in their photos after taking pictures of something, So I thought I would try it and hopefully catch something at random and I did,it was taken on a clear sunny day, I dont know what it is but it is very high in the sky, round, and spherical, and it also looks like it may have been moving in the picture. My first possible ufo picture. I will continue to take more pictures and hopefully get more in my pictures.
